21:50.893 --> 21:52.727
I was shocked when you said
Haggis was doing it in 90.

21:52.812 --> 21:54.562
Shocked. Didn't think
it was possible.

21:54.647 --> 21:57.440
So you must have thought it was really
impossible to do it in 65 days, huh?

21:57.525 --> 21:58.525
Mm-hmm.

21:58.609 --> 22:00.485
So essentially you sent
us on a fool's errand?

22:00.569 --> 22:02.821
- Well, a little bit.
We delivered.

22:02.905 --> 22:05.573
Oh, yes we did.
And we owe you. Thank you.

22:08.244 --> 22:09.619
Can't let you do it.

22:11.038 --> 22:14.749
- What do you mean?
- Well...

22:14.834 --> 22:17.210
You said if I was back
on November 1 st...

22:17.294 --> 22:20.255
Vince, I've got
a billion-dollar franchise to protect.

22:20.506 --> 22:22.340
Happy Meals, action figures.

22:22.425 --> 22:23.967
I can't risk all that
having my Aquaman

22:24.051 --> 22:26.594
doing three hours of blow
in every multiplex in the country.

22:26.846 --> 22:30.390
