and you said that you'd do this for me.

22:30.474 --> 22:31.516
- You gave me your word.
- I'm sorry.

22:31.600 --> 22:33.935
Alan, a man is only
as good as his word.

22:34.020 --> 22:36.980
Vince, it's just business.
Not personal.

22:37.565 --> 22:40.233
Oh. Just business.

22:43.029 --> 22:45.864
All right, then I want
20 million to do "A2"

22:46.115 --> 22:48.616
or I quit.
